        {
            "id": 6009010,
            "title": "精成科5月營收33.83億元年增81.77%創2007年來新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精成科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6191:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6191\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6191-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公布最新營收資訊，精成科 2025 年 5 月營收爲 33.83 億元，月增 7.35%，年增 81.77%，爲 2007 年來新高，主要爲精成科完成以 84 億元收購日商 PCB 廠 Lincstech 的 100% 股權，並於 4 月 8 日完成交割並挹注營收。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009010%2Fl%2F3ee201a235c09025af64f872cc5acc5b.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">精成科董事長焦佑衡。(鉅亨網記者張欽發攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精成科 2025 年 1-5 月營收 116.97 億元，年增 31.72%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精成科統計，併購 Lincstech 後 PCB 營收占比 75%，EMS 占 25%。產品組合增加伺服器、Probe Cards 探針卡與機器人、醫療產品等。同時，也使精成科的生產基地再經過此一併購案擴及新加坡，且更具 96 層的高階板生產能力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，精成科爲償還銀行借款，5 月 28 日並由董事會決議以發債加上辦理現增方式進行市場籌資以償還銀行借款，市場估計這兩筆籌資案合計募集金額達 30 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精成科董事會決議發行 2.5 萬張現增股且發行 10 億元無擔保可轉換公債，是今年以來 PCB 廠最大規模的市場籌資案，以精成科目前 47.43 億元的股本來看，精成科主管指出，發行 2.5 萬張的現增股對獲利的稀釋只有 5%，影響獲利並不大。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>精成科 2025 年第一季營收 51.63 億元，毛利率 20.21%，季減 3.53 個百分點，年減 6.93 個百分點，稅後純益 7.41 億元，季增 49.4%，年增 27.11%，每股純益 1.57 元。精成科認為，收購日商 PCB 廠 Lincstech 的 100% 股權後，固然其生產成本較高，但有其效益產生，且預估未來的精成科合併毛利率也將不致跌破首季今年首季的 20.21%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
